											message :"Dear Parent, <br> I am writing to inform you that your child, " + input.Student.Student_Name + ", was absent from school today in the Evening session, " + zoho.currentdate + ". We wanted to ensure you were made aware of their absence as soon as possible. " + " <br> If you could please provide a reason for your child's absence, we would appreciate it. This will help us ensure that we are meeting the needs of all our students. <br> Thank you for your continued support in helping us provide the best possible education for your child. <br> Sincerely, <br> Admin office <br> " + edu.School_Name
